                            <td class="p-3 text-muted-foreground">Minute column increment. 1 (default) lists every minute; 5/15 etc. list only multiples of the step.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="p-3 font-mono text-xs text-primary">SecondStep</td>
